TRAIT.name = "Freedom 2: Defender of the Barrier"
TRAIT.description = "For years, it was Freedom defending the Barrier from Monolith. In their absence, you are a good replacement.\nWhen in combat with hostile factions, you can spot tactical weaknesses and advantages. Once per round, you can give a single friendly 1 reroll on any roll they make. They can choose between the first roll and the reroll."
